sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant CL as CallsLink
    participant CP as CallsPopover
    participant API as pseudo-api

    U->>CL: hover
    Note over CL: 400ms timer
    CL->>API: fetchPseudoFile(fileStem)
    API-->>CL: content
    CL->>CP: show(content, position)
    U->>CP: hover (cancels grace timer)
    U->>CP: click
    CP->>U: navigate to file
    U->>CL: mouse leave
    Note over CL: 300ms grace
    CL->>CP: close